1
00:00:00,450 --> 00:00:04,781
Switching Docker runtimes shouldn't mean
rebuilding your local world.

2
00:00:04,950 --> 00:00:08,833
Images. Volumes. Networks.
Ports. Container state.

3
00:00:09,000 --> 00:00:14,611
Dory discovers Docker Desktop, OrbStack,
Colima, and other compatible sources.

4
00:00:14,780 --> 00:00:19,623
It reads first—checking capacity
and collisions before writing to Dory.

5
00:00:19,690 --> 00:00:24,490
Dory imports transactionally, verifies,
and never deletes the source.

6
00:00:24,560 --> 00:00:29,893
Dory. Your complete local Linux workspace.
Bring the work. Leave the lock behind.
